uzimelele ngobhoko unyawo ulubeke phezu kwedolo lomunye umlenze
nasi ke isivivinyo senu sesithathu futhi sokugcina
zemba zambulula izinsizwa ozibonayo angangingabazi ukuthi kukhona okuzixoshayo
abaholi babo babehamba nabo lapho beyophanga izinkomo behlasela amabhubesi
ilanga leli alishisi nje linomuntu phansi
lethiwe inkosi ayimlahli umuntu vuyiswa
lethiwe hhayi impela kunizumile ukufa vuyiswa
[n] uphuma nje nakuyena amehlo acwebe izinyembezi
wanquma futhi ukuthi uzoxolisa uma kufika kuleso simo
